{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.240", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.880", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an den Anfang unserer Debatte geh\u00f6rt die Aussage: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.840", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die allermeisten Eltern in Deutschland schaffen es auch im Falle einer schmerzhaften Trennung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einvernehmlich ein Betreuungsmodell zu vereinbaren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.880", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Betreuungsmodell, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem die Kinder und die beiden Eltern gut leben k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.880", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen Eltern geb\u00fchrt unsere Anerkennung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie sich in einer schwierigen Situation selbst zur\u00fccknehmen und das Wohl des Kindes oder der Kinder an die erste Stelle stellen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das wollen auch wir als Gesetzgeber tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.040", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen das Wohl der Kinder an die erste Stelle setzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.440", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss klar sein und klar bleiben: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entscheidungen im Bereich des Umgangsrechts sind kein verl\u00e4ngerter Arm der bitteren Auseinandersetzungen zwischen zwei Eltern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.080", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was gerecht f\u00fcr die Eltern ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.880", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Frage muss lauten: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.400", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was dient den betroffenen Kindern?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und dann gibt es leider auch eben die F\u00e4lle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.880", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen die Entfremdung der gescheiterten Partner so gro\u00df ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.280", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine Einigung \u00fcber Ort und Dauer des Aufenthalts der Kinder unm\u00f6glich ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.160", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Recht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.400", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerechtigkeit und Hilfe sucht man dann bei der Justiz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.520", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur \u00fcber diese seltenen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.720", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verfahrenen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.040", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zerstrittenen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.960", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "perspektivlosen Konstellationen beraten wir als Gesetzgeber und eben nicht \u00fcber F\u00e4lle von Eltern wie die von Marie und Maximilian, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.360", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie eben geschildert haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.960", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen alles wunderbar l\u00e4uft und man sich einigen kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.640", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schon beim ersten Blick auf diese schwierigen Familiensituationen muss doch jedem klar sein: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.800", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf kann man nicht mit einem Regelfall antworten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.680", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann diese F\u00e4lle nicht \u00fcber einen Kamm scheren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.680", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So hat es auch der Bundesgerichtshof in seiner Entscheidung Anfang letzten Jahres betont. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.120", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er hat entschieden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Wechselmodell auch gegen den Willen eines Partners angeordnet werden kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.000", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.120", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es dem Kindeswohl am besten dient."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.080", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Kinder bedeutet das Wechselmodell konkret, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie in den beiden Haushalten der getrennten Eltern zeitlich ann\u00e4hernd gleichwertig betreut werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann im Einzelfall die beste L\u00f6sung sein; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.160", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es muss nicht immer die beste L\u00f6sung sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.680", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.680", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Kinderbetreuung nach der Trennung von Eltern unterliegt einem gesellschaftlichen Wandel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.400", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutsche Familiengerichte m\u00fcssen heute, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.040", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im 21.\u00a0Jahrhundert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.520", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wirklich nicht immer einfach noch davon ausgehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Kinder bei der Mutter automatisch immer besser aufgehoben sind,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.640", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn das Modell immer noch das meistgelebte in Deutschland ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.600", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.080", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau hinzusehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.280", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich die Einzelf\u00e4lle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sonderf\u00e4lle in der Gerichtspraxis genau anzuschauen und zu \u00fcberlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.200", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob sich daraus ein gesetzgeberischer Handlungsbedarf ergibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das steht auch im Koalitionsvertrag."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.360", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Auswirkungen des Wechselmodells auf die Kinder werden zurzeit auch wissenschaftlich untersucht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.200", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einig ist man sich unter den Wissenschaftlern schon heute, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ein st\u00e4ndiger Wechsel des Aufenthaltsortes der Kinder nur dann eine positive Wirkung entfalten kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.720", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn einige wichtige Voraussetzungen erf\u00fcllt sind: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.040", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Eltern m\u00fcssen in r\u00e4umlicher N\u00e4he zueinander wohnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.920", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Arbeitszeiten der Eltern m\u00fcssen sich an die wechselnde Kinderbetreuung anpassen lassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr dieses wirklich kostenintensive Modell m\u00fcssen die n\u00f6tigen Finanzmittel zur Verf\u00fcgung stehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.320", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Eltern m\u00fcssen in einem konstruktiven Kommunikationskontakt zueinander stehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00e4ufig hilft es bei familiengerichtlichen Entscheidungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen Blick auf die Zeit vor der Trennung zu werfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn die Eltern sich da bereits beide um das Kind gek\u00fcmmert haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.560", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ist das sicherlich eine gute Prognose f\u00fcr den Erfolg eines Wechselmodells. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Lebenswirklichkeit ist das aber trotz allem Wunschdenken l\u00e4ngst noch nicht immer der Fall. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.720", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "V\u00e4ter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.240", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die erfolgreich um Zeit und Aufenthalt ihres Kindes gestritten haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.360", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann aber die Erziehung ihres Kindes der neuen Partnerin \u00fcberlassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.320", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind nur ein Beispiel f\u00fcr ein falsch verstandenes Wechselmodell."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.680", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um es klar zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.440", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Engagierte V\u00e4ter m\u00fcssen ihren Platz bei und ihre Zeit mit ihren Kindern haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.040", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genauso wie engagierte M\u00fctter ihn haben m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.680", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was Familien in Trennungssituationen hilft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.960", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind gut ausgebildete Familienrichter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen unabh\u00e4ngige Gutachter und Verfahrensbeist\u00e4nde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "304.240", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir sollten unsere Familiengerichte darin st\u00e4rken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "304.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "308.360", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am Einzelfall orientierte Entscheidungen zu treffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "308.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.600", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "statt neue Regelf\u00e4lle zu definieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "310.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.200", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es die FDP-Fraktion vorschl\u00e4gt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "314.320", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber seien wir ehrlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "314.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.680", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am Ende aller elterlichen Streitigkeiten geht es h\u00e4ufig auch um die Frage der Finanzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "321.560", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Frage des Unterhalts."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "321.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "322.800", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommen Sie bitte zum Schluss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "322.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.400", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden uns deshalb als Koalition anschauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "325.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "328.880", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir den Unterhaltsbedarf und Selbstbehalt verbindlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
